sale day
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:in country towns, the day on which a farm livestock sale is held
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: also saleday
